{"title":"(15) implementacion-amb-sysmayal2 - Raven","url":"https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/raven/AMB-Wellness/AMB-Wellness-implementacion-amb-sysmayal2","summary":"This is a technical support and implementation chat channel for AMB-Wellsness on the Raven ERP system (ERPNext). The channel contains discussions about sales order processing, quotation management, and manufacturing workflows. Key topics include syncing sales orders from quotations (SO-00756 for Barentz Italia S.p.A), pipeline diagnostics for quotations, AI bot commands for ERP operations, troubleshooting work order issues (MFG-WO-04226 related to Item 0334 - Innovaloe Aloe Vera Gel), and creating work orders from sales orders. The channel also documents a root cause analysis for a manufacturing issue caused by missing valuation rates in the item master, with lessons learned about pre-flight checks before manufacturing operations.","key_points":["Sales order SO-00756-BARENTZ Italia S.p.A was synced from quotation SAL-QTN-2024-00756 with payment terms changed from 30 to 60 days","Pipeline diagnosis showed SAL-QTN-2024-00756 (Barentz Italia) at $35,385 USD and SAL-QTN-2024-00763 (Lorand Laboratories) at $107,884.42 USD","Work order MFG-WO-04226 had corrupted Stock Ledger Entries due to missing Valuation Rate on Item 0334","Root cause: Item 0334 had NO Valuation Rate set, causing manufacturing entries to fail","Solution involved cancelling stock entries in correct order, setting valuation rate to 104.00, then re-running transfer and finish commands","Three work orders were created from SO-00763-LORAND LABORATORIES for item 0803","AI bot provides capabilities for sales order follow-up, manufacturing workflows, BOM management, and document actions","Lessons learned include the importance of pre-flight checks for valuation rate before manufacturing and proper cancel order sequence"],"relevant_links":["https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/app/sales-order/SO-00756-BARENTZ Italia S.p.A","https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/app/quotation/SAL-QTN-2024-00756","https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/app/quotation/SAL-QTN-2024-00763","https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/app/work-order/MFG-WO-04226","https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/app/sales-order/SO-00752-LEGOSAN AB","https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/app/work-order/MFG-WO-04326","https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/app/work-order/MFG-WO-04426","https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/app/work-order/MFG-WO-04526","https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/app/work-order/MFG-WO-04626","https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/app/bom/BOM-0334-005"],"file_name":"amb_wellness_implementacion_raven_channel.json"}
